The Bourne Identity;;93;;84;;PG-13;;The story of a man (Matt Damon), salvaged, near death, from the ocean by an Italian fishing boat. When he recuperates, the man suffers from total amnesia, without identity or background... except for a range of extraordinary talents in fighting, linguistic skills and self-defense that speak of a dangerous past. He sets out on a desperate search-assisted by the initially rebellious Marie (Franka Potente) - to discover who he really is, and why he's being lethally pursued by assassins.;;Mystery & thriller,Action;;Doug Liman;;2002;;Matt Damon,Franka Potente,Chris Cooper,Clive Owen,Brian Cox,Adewale Akinnuoye-Agbaje,Gabriel Mann,Walton Goggins,Josh Hamilton,Julia Stiles,Orso Maria Guerrini,Tim Dutton;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bourne_identity